@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">About Brew Haven</h1>
            <p class="lead">Crafting exceptional coffee experiences since 2015</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
            <img src="/images/about-coffee-shop.jpg" alt="Our Coffee Shop" class="img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm" style="object-fit: cover; height: 400px; width: 100%;">
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="h3 mb-4">Our Story</h2>
            <p>Brew Haven began with a simple passion: to create a space where coffee lovers could enjoy exceptional brews in a warm, welcoming environment. Founded in 2015, our journey started with a small cafe in District 1, Ho Chi Minh City.</p>
            <p>What sets us apart is our commitment to quality, sustainability, and community. We source our beans directly from farmers around the world, ensuring fair prices while securing the finest harvests. Each cup we serve represents our dedication to the craft of coffee.</p>
            <p>Over the years, we've grown from a single location to multiple cafes across Vietnam, but our mission remains unchanged: to serve exceptional coffee with genuine hospitality.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-12 text-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="h3">Our Values</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-cup-hot" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #8b5a2b;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Quality</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">We never compromise on quality. From bean selection to brewing techniques, excellence is our standard.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-globe" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #8b5a2b;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Sustainability</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">We're committed to environmentally and socially responsible practices across our entire operation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-people" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #8b5a2b;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Community</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">We believe coffee brings people together. Our cafes are designed to foster connection and community.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
            <img src="/images/coffee-team.jpg" alt="Our Team" class="img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm" style="object-fit: cover; height: 400px; width: 100%;">
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
            <h2 class="h3 mb-4">Our Team</h2>
            <p>Behind every great cup of coffee is a dedicated team of professionals who are passionate about what they do. From our skilled baristas to our thoughtful managers, each member brings their unique talents to create the Brew Haven experience.</p>
            <p>Our team undergoes rigorous training to ensure they're knowledgeable about our products and can provide exceptional service. Many of our staff members have been with us for years, growing alongside our business.</p>
            <p>We believe in creating a positive work environment where creativity and initiative are encouraged, and where everyone feels valued and respected.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h2 class="h3 mb-4">Visit Us Today</h2>
            <p class="lead">We'd love to welcome you to one of our locations and share our passion for coffee with you.</p>
            <a href="/Home/Locations" class="btn btn-outline-brown mt-3">Find a Location Near You</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .btn-outline-brown {
        color: #8b5a2b;
        border-color: #8b5a2b;
    }

    .btn-outline-brown:hover {
        color: white;
        background-color: #8b5a2b;
        border-color: #8b5a2b;
    }
</style>